trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionType"></xref> that represents the resource redirection type.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionType"> </xref> som representerer omadressering ressurstypen.

trans-unit.source: A resource redirection indicates the requested resource has been relocated to the specified location(s).
trans-unit.target: En ressurs-omadressering angir den forespurte ressursen er flyttet til den angitte startside.

trans-unit.source: If one location is specified, then this maps to HTTP status code 301 (Moved Permanently) or 307 (Temporary Redirect), depending on the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionDuration> selected.
trans-unit.target: Hvis én plassering er angitt, vil dette tilordnes til HTTP-statuskode 301 (flyttet permanent) eller 307 (midlertidig omadressere), avhengig av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionDuration>valgte.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionDuration>

trans-unit.source: If multiple locations are provided, then this maps to the 300 (Multiple Choices) HTTP status code.
trans-unit.target: Hvis flere steder angis, tilordner dette til 300 (flere valg) HTTP-statuskoden.

trans-unit.source: This is the default value for <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionType>.
trans-unit.target: Dette er standardverdien for <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionType>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RedirectionType>

trans-unit.source: A use intermediary redirection indicates the requested resource must be accessed through an intermediate service, for example, an HTTP proxy server.
trans-unit.target: En mellomliggende omadressering Bruk angir den forespurte ressursen må åpnes via en mellomliggende tjeneste, for eksempel en HTTP-proxy-server.

trans-unit.source: This corresponds to the HTTP status code 305 (Use Proxy)
